article.description: — Joseph Octave had 17 points as Air Force beat Texas Southern 61-57 on Wednesday night.
article.headline: Octave carries Air Force past Texas Southern 61-57
article.linkText: Octave carries Air Force past Texas Southern 61-57
article.story: AIR FORCE ACADEMY, Colo. -- — Joseph Octave had 17 points as Air Force beat Texas Southern 61-57 on Wednesday night. A.J. Walker had 13 points for Air Force (2-1). Camden Vander Zwaag added 10 points as did Jake Heidbreder. John Walker III had 16 points for the Tigers (0-4). Joirdon Karl Nicholas added 10 points ad did Justin Hopkins. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
